# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in real values. `.env` is gitignored and
# hidden from Obsidian — secrets NEVER live in notes. Scripts reference these
# keys by NAME only (e.g. os.environ.get("SUMMARY_API_KEY")).
#
# The default digest-url workflow needs NO secrets. This key is only used if you
# enable the optional LLM-summary step inside tools/fetch-url.py.

# SUMMARY_API_KEY=
